divs: Sighting DetailsTaking pic of airliner on way to TIA caught an unknown object that wasn't seen while taking pic. Scanned for birds before snaping pic.Had a real banner week for objects in sky using a reconditioned camera with a viewfinder so my aim is better. Also for change of pace another pic taken a few days before of airplane with white dot in pic which at first thought was something unusual but have since decided it was daytime pic of Venus after all.Just wanted to show you that you can see Venus in daytime.
